title: Spanish, Catalan police embrace in Barcelona
description:
(5 Oct 2017) Spanish and Catalan police embraced each other as the former left the town of Pineda del Mar, Barcelona, on Thursday.
Dozens of locals supporting the Spanish central government bid goodbye to the Spanish National Police as they left the hotel where they were staying over the last several days.
